  <body>
    <p>The <ph keyref="product"/> XSLT/XQuery Debugger allows you to interrupt XSLT/XQuery
      processing to gather information about variables and processor execution at particular points.
      To ensure <term>breakpoints</term> are persistent between work sessions, they are saved at
      project level. You can set a maximum of 100 <term>breakpoints</term> per project.</p>
  </body>
